TopicTitle: List of Mods Compatible with KSP 1.3

Articles.Content:
Hello there, I am the guy that (almost) never posts, but I wanted to help the community at least a bit, so here's a list of which mods have been updated to work with KSP 1.3

Disclaimer : Not all of the listed mods have been tested. Most have just been updated and I included them here. Reply with the name of any "compatible" mod crashing the game and I'l remove it, or with a mod not included here and I'll add it

List of mods in the spoiler, sorted by alphabet in sub-spoilers. WARNING: It's really long

Of course, but at least 80% of those will still work, despite being outdated. I am personally still using some mods written for 0.90

Maybe parts mods from .90, but there's no way you're using any plugins from that far back. 

I had 107 mods before the update, only the big ones like RT, scansat, and KAS screwed up for me. It all really depends on what is modified in the update. Ones that are incredibly intricate such as the previously mentioned rely heavily on how the code in KSP is phrased, once that changes, things go bad
